org.apache.flex.swc

Class SWCDepends

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.swc.SWCDepends

  • public class SWCDepends
extends Object
    swcdepends command line utility. Use this utility to see the dependency order of all SWCs in your configuration. You can also see: - the swcs a swc is dependent on (on by default). - the scripts that are causing the dependency (off by default). - the dependency types of the scripts (off by default).
